<HL>
   Marketing:
   Cost of Cheese
   May Turn Pizza
   Into Pricey Pie
   ----
   By Richard Gibson and Scott Kilman
   Staff Reporters of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
08/26/91
</DATE>
